{"title":"塞外题壁——街头诗八首","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞外题壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——街头诗八首\t田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞外题壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红的太阳是人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿的长城是树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满地星是水井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗和壁画是城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（写在商都县城的墙壁上）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商都赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枝跃进花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开在商都县。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树是草原人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树是总路线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶子是草原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花是水和电。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这枝跃进花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是商都县。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（写在商都县城的墙壁上）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水是一枝花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花开草原乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水是一件宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商都宝最好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水是一支歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱的千年乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（写在不冻河水库工地）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千井赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢钻好像是铁树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰灯好像是银灯。〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁树栽在井中心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球打开千道门。〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商都县在严寒季节挖泉时，社员们用冰块做成灯，挂在井下，以便在井下抢水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨树赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲远走千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨树来到草原；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁路结成长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨树栽到天边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天边还有个天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新栽杨树一片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沼气赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沼气来到草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草地更有朝气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城关社好手艺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫沼气上了电机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沼气照在城里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似锦囊妙计；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和月亮比美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和风砂争高低。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（写在城关镇合作社）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清泉社赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井水一千眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜水亿万担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担上千井水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早日下江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南是何处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮山是江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（写在清泉社的墙壁上）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠高勿素乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾上风，引上水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水泉岭要发电。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步跨过草原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两步走到江南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三步奔到海边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要吓倒美利坚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（写在高勿素乡的墙壁上）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}